# 🔹 If-Else Case Study Questions (Java)

This folder contains Java programs based on **if-else conditional statements**.  
All programs are designed as case study questions to help beginners understand decision-making logic in Java.

---

## 📚 Topics Covered

- Basic If Statement
- If–Else Conditions
- Else-If Ladder
- Nested If Statements
- Logical Operators (&&, ||, !)
- Real-life Case Study Problems

---

## 🧠 Case Study Programs Included

- Leap Year Checker
- Grade Calculator
- Average Marks Evaluation
- Number Positive/Negative Check
- Even or Odd Number
- Largest of Three Numbers
- Pass or Fail System
- Percentage Classification

---

## 🎯 Learning Objectives

After completing these programs, you will be able to:

- Understand conditional logic in Java
- Apply decision-making statements
- Solve real-world programming problems
- Improve logical thinking skills

---

